Commentary: OUT! RUN OUT! A huge mix-up in the middle and that cost Sri Lanka dearly here! This is short and around off, Dimuth Karunaratne moves back and punches it wide of sweeper covers for a run, Nishan Madushka turns around for the second and his partner initially responds but then sends him back when he is already halfway down the track, Hasan Mahmud picks up and fires in a perfect throw right at the top of the stumps where Litton Das collects and breaks the stumps quickly. The replay shows that Madushka is well short of his crease. Bangladesh finally get their first breakthrough!
